title: catalog
text:
catalog





Name
Description




Catalog
Represents a catalog of products.


Category
Represents a category of products.


Embedding
Represents an embedding.


Product
Represents a product.


Vibe
Represents a vibe.





catalog.Catalog(self, description, products=None)
Represents a catalog of products.
Attributes: - id: The unique identifier of the catalog. - version: The version of the catalog. - description: The description of the catalog. - products: The list of products in the catalog.



catalog.Category(self, description, url, embeddings)
Represents a category of products.
Attributes: - description: The description of the category. - url: The URL of the category. - vibes: The list of vibes associated with the category.



catalog.Embedding(self, v)
Represents an embedding.
Attributes: - v : the vector embedding



catalog.Product(self, description, url, categories=None, vibes=None)
Represents a product.
Attributes: - id: The unique identifier of the product. - description: The description of the product. - url: The URL of the product. - categories: The list of categories the product belongs to.



catalog.Vibe(self, description, imageBase64, url, embeddings)
Represents a vibe.
Attributes: - id: The unique identifier of the vibe. - description: The description of the vibe. - imageBase64: The base64 encoded image of the vibe. - url: The URL of the vibe. - embeddings: The list of embeddings associated with the vibe.
